<p class="ql-align-center">说出来吓死你！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想要完整的听完这首曲子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>需要 639 年！！！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200817/5f2ae9c198fe46839cac95d411f30d0c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从2001年9月起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这首“慢到极点”的曲子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经在德国某个废弃的教堂内</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">演奏了3年了~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总共演奏了5个音符</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>而且还要再演奏636年！！！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200817/ad86d9425daa431bb0178a1a6269ebb4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">预定的这一场演出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将于2640年结束</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而下一次出现音乐时间是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020 年9月5日</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给你们瞅瞅这首曲子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">部分演奏时间线图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/ccc62d2fd53f44cdb1d0d9908d00988b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小犀牛需要通过吃妈妈的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“大便”</strong>来获取益生菌~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太惨了~~~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200817/26601acb8a0e48eba478e7413fdb5fe5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你一定不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Lady Gaga其实是“拍立得”的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">创意总监!</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/2d2b3019ecc649f9bd5406ca4d4531de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>04</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国女王的手提包其实是一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“肢体语言沟通装置”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女王用手提包来向手下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传达隐秘和无声的讯息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/0dcfb8cc2bbe4b87a65325969ccd6037.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果她已经和客人谈完话了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就会将手提包从一只手换到另一侧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后她的侍从就会客气的中断会话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200817/3aacf2a094b2491a93d2a36f87b464e7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>05</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你使劲掐一掐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">胳膊肘那块肉试试</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你会发现它的敏感度很低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都不怎么疼~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200817/5b0ea8c762c5495f9c4f459f3f875922.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>06</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用手指靠近眉心下面一点的位置</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是鼻梁上边，两眼中间的位置</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但别碰到哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200817/87563d9c87ee4c9983da01a74c88e53c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你会有一种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说不出道不明的感觉~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200817/8495be52714c4f86907915727e9f79b9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>07</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于人类来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最危险的事情绝对是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>把闹钟关掉以后，又闭上眼睛了！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200817/dad025c4a3854fbbb7eb56aa16ced656.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为这是目前人类</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想要穿越未来的“唯一方法”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闭眼5秒钟你会神奇的发现！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自己成功抵达到了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2小时后的未来！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200817/1602d2bd216544fab0f3b961c063b473.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>08</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">五音不全的你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">应该庆幸自己不是菲律宾人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们的法律规定：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>唱国歌跑调的人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将被判处 2 年以下有期徒刑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和 2000 多美元罚款......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200817/c923b499c8884a7f8bca28cf5dde71c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>09</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然猫头鹰的眼睛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很大！很有神！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但实际上却是不能转动的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过，它们的脖子异常的灵活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>能旋转270度！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以只能依靠脖子来转动~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/9ef83e954a63430896f210df6cc99f6c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>10</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有狐臭的其实才是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“正常人”！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为大多数没有狐臭的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靠的都是基因变异！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200817/c0945e88a33140c4b737f5103d007134.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要知道， 有狐臭的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实是很多的！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">根本就不是“极少数人”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">附上参考图(蓝色：有；橙色：无) </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200817/e17e0d1136f94228b20bb04295dc0210.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>11</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>公鸡是没有丁丁的！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它和母鸡交配的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">需要互相把彼此的泄殖腔孔口对着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后公鸡才能把自己的“小蝌蚪”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">排到母鸡体内……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200817/656817b0fb8a4c789d868ed95da1c617.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>12</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你看到可爱的人或东西</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是不是总有一种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想要去捏一下的冲动？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这可能是一种叫做</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“萌系侵略冲动”</strong>的病喔~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当你面对的东西越可爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大脑情绪反应就越积极</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了避免你被“萌死”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是大脑就会产生一些相反的情绪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来维持平衡！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因此你就会想去做一些破坏性的行为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（比如捏、揉）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200817/86e8c5f671504c10b42ee07cd307d7c8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>13</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然很恶心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但还是想告诉你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人“指甲"其实也是一种药材</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/9eacaf29c5cb48b1be70c5bbd24c3ed2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃过的宝宝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>麻烦私信我，来说说感想......</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/e189a8ccb22e46b69ba669478dc58035.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/e189a8ccb22e46b69ba669478dc58035.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/e189a8ccb22e46b69ba669478dc58035.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>14</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世界上最感人的“兄弟情”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绝对是“灰鲸”了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为它们和对象交配的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>是需要好兄弟来协助的！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200817/8a00f62c31c243c5ac8d5a538c23b3fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灰鲸由于体重太重</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">交配时还需要第三头雄鲸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从最下面托起雌性的背部</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才能顺利完成<strong>“造鱼大业”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/8e2032a5c11746debac4ec9d604bd712.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>15</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“嗯”并不读「en」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在字典上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它只有这几种读音：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>ǹg，ńg，ňg，ǹ，ń，ň</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200817/ee8a5aaa0d7844b9bd5cb4065f1f2ded.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>16</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">床笫（zǐ）之欢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并不是床第之欢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（笫：竹编的床席）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200817/d7786432054049068b0ede3e89a994b1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>17</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行为心理学家总结出了一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">非常有意思的现象：</p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>“8.2秒决定男生是否被女生吸引”</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/6920f9ffb29c4c0ab650d2effe7b9186.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果一对男女初次见面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男生花了8.2秒去看这个女生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有极大的可能是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个男生被女生吸引了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至是爱上了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这就是所谓的一见钟情！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>18</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你有没有发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在我们国家，天蝎座的人最多！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为天蝎座的受孕时间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大多是在公历的一月底前后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这个时候正巧是春节假期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">众多离家在外的夫妻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以在这时团聚在一起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200817/4f92a07085b1425aa0a1e6dbe1f1c68d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为在父母辈时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文化娱乐项目还不咋丰富</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是很多夫妻都把精力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">投向了“造人工程”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因此新年就变成“造人高峰期”了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你算算日子~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/04381a74f0904ce691611531e26737d9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另外，你还会发现！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大多中小学教师家庭的孩子中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>金牛座的几率</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也比全行业平均水平高一些！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是因为辛苦的老师们在暑假时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才精力关心自己的下一代问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200817/90556921f4054a0dbb4a7e027b3dba02.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>19</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 一次，卓别林参加了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“卓别林相似者模仿大赛”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">得了第三名......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真的非常好奇第一名是哪位~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200817/c9c5e1e5e2bd4011ad35030df14c1490.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>20</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">台湾省教育部门正式认定：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">「尴尬」是可以读作「jiān jiè」的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/51280d04462a4665aa38d5ab480eb4a0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
